Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要唱什么歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要唱什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 我也口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不唱歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是想交友才参加的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是要参加联谊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你害羞的话 我会陪你一起唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 选歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.48,Default-TOP,NTP,0,0,0,,等 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这样说的话 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更想使坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变成这样的话 该怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那男的途中就变成宇佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的性骚扰妄想一定有一百零八式的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我的妄想 妄想的对象也不想是其他男人
